data.description: Berkey Home Builders offers this gorgeous ranch home with plenty of upgrades and a 3 car garage. Pond view. Kids can walk to Clay Elementary! Enjoy the bike trail right next door. Granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and birch cabinets in the spacious eat-in kitchen. Hardwood floors, frieze carpet and ceramic tile throughout. Vaulted ceiling and fireplace in the great room. Tray ceiling in master bedroom as well as a huge walk-in closet and spacious bathroom with a double vanity. Basement is finished with an additional bedroom and bathroom, gorgeous fireplace, and wet bar.  Cement board siding with stone accents. Energy efficient!
